    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-10-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-10-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="683"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d683">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">795.00/10–1650: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Korea</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Drumright</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Seoul</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-10-16">October 16,
                            1950.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received October 16—5:08 a. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>265. In receipt this morning to Deptel 191, October 12, I endeavored see Home
                    Minister but finding him out of town I went to see President Rhee and made
                    representations to him re utilization of <gloss target="#t_ROK1">ROK</gloss>
                    police in North Korea. Rhee did not receive representations with good grace, his
                    attitude was one of defiance of UN and determination to incorporate North Korea
                    into <gloss target="#t_ROK1">ROK</gloss> as speedily as possible. I urged him to
                    avoid by word and deed acts which would put him in bad order [<hi rend="italic"
                        >odor?</hi>] with UN. He assured me he would hold his tongue until he had
                    chance to confer with Ambassador Muccio who is expected here Wednesday.<note
                        n="1" xml:id="d683fn1">October 18.</note>
                </p>
                <p>I am awaiting return Home Minister in order ascertain definitely status of police
                    in east coast area. All other north of parallel appear definitely under
                    authority Unified Command.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Drumright</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
